HEADWORD: Prestidigital
<hw>Pres`ti*dig"i*tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Nimble-fingered; having fingers fit for prestidigitation, or
juggling.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧His <xex>prestidigital</xex>
hand.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Charles Reade.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
